'''亞洲青少年田徑錦標賽'''（{{lang-en|'''Asian Youth Athletics Championships'''}}）是由[[亞洲田徑總會|亞洲田徑總會]]所舉辦的青少年洲際性賽事。首屆於[[卡達|卡達]][[多哈|多哈]]進行<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gulf-times.com/sport/192/details/436843/doha-ready-to-host-1st-asian-youth-athletics-championship|title=Doha ready to host 1st Asian Youth Athletics Championship|publisher=Gulf Times|date=2015-04-27|accessdate=2015-05-09|archive-date=2015-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518085441/http://www.gulf-times.com/sport/192/details/436843/doha-ready-to-host-1st-asian-youth-athletics-championship|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

